{"reels-packages":[{"question":"How long does filming take?","answer":"A single filming day takes about 6 hours. During that time, we capture material for 3-8 Reels videos."},{"question":"Do I need to have scripts ready?","answer":"No! In the Growth and Dominance packages, script creation is included. Together we'll brainstorm topics that will engage your audience."},{"question":"How quickly will I receive the finished videos?","answer":"Initial previews are usually within 3-5 days. Final version after your feedback."},{"question":"Can I use the videos on other networks?","answer":"Yes! Vertical videos (9:16) work great on Instagram, TikTok, YouTube Shorts, and LinkedIn."}],"creative-production":[{"question":"How much does a commercial spot cost?","answer":"It depends on the scope of the project. Basic spot from £950, complex production with actors and locations from £1,800. I'll always give you the price upfront."},{"question":"How long does production take?","answer":"From the first call to the final video usually 2-4 weeks. It depends on the complexity of the project."},{"question":"Do you provide actors and locations?","answer":"Yes, I can provide complete production including casting, locations, and equipment."},{"question":"Can you film a TV commercial?","answer":"Yes, for large projects I collaborate with SocialVids, who have experience with TV commercials."}],"event-video":[{"question":"Do you film outside of London?","answer":"Yes, I film across the UK and internationally (primarily Prague)."},{"question":"How quickly will I receive the event video?","answer":"I offer express delivery - short clips for social media the same evening, complete aftermovie within 5-7 days."},{"question":"Do I need more videographers?","answer":"For smaller events, I am enough. For large events, I can provide a full team."},{"question":"Does the price include drone footage?","answer":"Drone footage is for an extra fee. We'll discuss this during the consultation."}],"live-stream":[{"question":"What connection do we need?","answer":"Ideally a stable internet connection with at least 10 Mbps upload. I can also provide a backup 4G/5G connection."},{"question":"Where can we broadcast?","answer":"YouTube, Facebook, LinkedIn, Zoom, or your own platform. We can broadcast to multiple platforms simultaneously."},{"question":"What if the internet fails?","answer":"I always have a backup connection and local recording. Even if the stream drops, the video is not lost."},{"question":"How many cameras do you use?","answer":"It depends on the project. Basic setup = 2 cameras, for large conferences up to 4-5 cameras + vision mixer."}],"post-production":[{"question":"Can you edit my own footage?","answer":"Yes! Send me your material and I'll turn it into a professional video."},{"question":"How long does editing take?","answer":"It depends on the length and complexity. A short Reels video (60s) = 1-2 days. A longer video (5-10 min) = 3-5 days."},{"question":"Does the price include music?","answer":"Yes, I use licensed music from libraries I subscribe to. If you want a specific song, we can purchase it."},{"question":"How many revisions do I get?","answer":"Usually 2 rounds of revisions. If you need more, we can agree on it."}],"voiceover":[{"question":"How quickly will I receive the recording?","answer":"I deliver most orders within 24 hours. If it's urgent, I can even do it within a few hours."},{"question":"Can I hear samples?","answer":"Yes! On this page you will find audio samples from my projects (Prazdroj, ČSOB, Oreo)."},{"question":"What formats do you deliver?","answer":"MP3, WAV, or any format you need. Always in high quality."},{"question":"Can you do dubbing too?","answer":"Yes, I also do dubbing for videos, e-learning courses, or animations."}],"ugc":[{"question":"How much does one UGC video cost?","answer":"The price depends on the length, number of videos (packages are more cost-effective), and production requirements. Contact me for a price list."},{"question":"Do I need to send the product?","answer":"Yes, for an authentic video, I need to have the product physically with me. I can send it back after filming."},{"question":"How soon will the video be ready?","answer":"I typically deliver the first preview within 3-5 business days after receiving the product."},{"question":"Does the price include advertising rights?","answer":"Yes, the price usually includes rights for use in ads (Usage Rights) for 12 months."}],"international-event-video":[{"question":"Do you charge extra for travel?","answer":"No hidden fees. All travel costs (flights, hotel, meals) are included in the quoted price upfront."},{"question":"How far in advance should I book?","answer":"For international events, we recommend 4-6 weeks. Rush bookings possible subject to availability."},{"question":"Do you have insurance for international work?","answer":"Yes, I carry liability insurance valid across the EU. I can provide a certificate on request."},{"question":"What if our event is in multiple cities?","answer":"I offer bundle discounts for multi-city tours. 3+ cities = 15% discount. Get in touch for a custom quote."},{"question":"Can you handle livestreaming internationally?","answer":"Yes, I can livestream from any location with stable internet. A test stream is always done in advance."},{"question":"What equipment do you travel with?","answer":"Professional cinema cameras, wireless audio, LED lights, and gimbals. All packed in carry-on luggage for reliability — no checked baggage risks."},{"question":"What if something goes wrong (delayed flight, etc.)?","answer":"I always arrive 1 day before the event for scouting. I carry backup equipment and am insured against cancellations."}],"event-moderator":[{"question":"What languages can you moderate in?","answer":"I'm fluent in English and Czech, with basic German. I can switch seamlessly between languages during the same event."},{"question":"How do you prepare for an event?","answer":"I research all speakers, topics, and the audience 1-2 weeks in advance. I prepare custom questions, review the schedule, and coordinate with the AV team."},{"question":"Can you moderate virtual/hybrid events?","answer":"Yes, I have experience with Zoom, Teams, and StreamYard. I can manage both in-person and virtual audiences simultaneously."},{"question":"What types of events do you moderate?","answer":"Tech conferences, corporate summits, panel discussions, product launches, awards ceremonies, and webinars. Primarily B2B events."},{"question":"Do you also provide event video coverage?","answer":"Yes! I can moderate your event AND arrange video coverage. This combo ensures your moderator is camera-aware, making the final video look even better."}],"corporate-actor":[{"question":"What types of corporate videos can you act in?","answer":"Training/e-learning videos, product demonstrations, brand spokesperson roles, testimonial videos, and corporate explainer content."},{"question":"Can you work with a teleprompter?","answer":"Yes, I'm proficient with teleprompters and can deliver naturally while reading scripts. This speeds up production significantly."},{"question":"Do you provide wardrobe?","answer":"I have a professional wardrobe suitable for corporate settings. For specific brand requirements, we can discuss in advance."},{"question":"What usage rights are included?","answer":"Standard 12-month usage rights for digital and print marketing are included. Extended licensing for broadcast or longer terms is available."}]}